lead_paragraph: Wales manager still Chris Coleman has warned his team against complacency ahead of this month's European Championship in France, following a slump in performances after they sealed qualification for the tournament.

headline.print_headline: Coleman Frets Over Wales Form Dip Since Euro Qualification
